==={{initialism}}===
'''TLDR'''

#{{internet}} too [[long]]; didn't [[read]]

====Usage notes====
*'''TLDR''' is used as a standard reply to '''[[RTFM]]'''.
*It is also used as a response on message boards when a user posts a long or boring message.